{
  "stem": "7177.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one of the people who was a salesperson there is Ben Fromm, who lives about 15 minutes away from me right here in Beverly [NON-ENGLISH], Los Angeles.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was one of the people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a traveling salesperson, and I was in the store.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we would sell ladies and gentleman's clothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was-- it got worse and worse and more difficult each and every time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But nobody can--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you had to give them everything that was silver or whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Gold, silver, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Later on, I don't remember exactly, but we-- we ended up with very, very little, I should say.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember all the things that we hand to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they would come and gather them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we could not go to a store.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had to-- we only could go to a store, I think, between 3:00 and 5:00.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Which if you have to go to, and the butcher, and the grocery, and the market.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was no such a thing as a market.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You go-- you go to all these different stores, so you couldn't-- you did not have very, very much time to run the errands.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My father, fortunately enough for us, he usually ran our errands.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it-- but it got-- I think we just took things as they came.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We-- well, we knew that we couldn't do anything about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, we didn't really fear for our lives, because we were all trained in doing labor in the field, if it had to be.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we thought with my father's-- what he would call an [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
